Fuck that.

735
01:07:35,852 --> 01:07:37,372
<i>Shit!</i>

736
01:07:38,452 --> 01:07:40,012
- <i>What?
- Fuck!</i>

737
01:07:40,572 --> 01:07:43,412
<i>Stay back, stay back!</i>

738
01:07:43,492 --> 01:07:44,812
<i>Get back!</i>

739
01:07:50,772 --> 01:07:53,452
<i>Go, go, go! Get away!</i>

740
01:07:56,652 --> 01:07:58,492
<i>For fuck's sake, move!</i>

