individual responsibility..."

751
01:09:09,332 --> 01:09:10,532
Is it all like this?

752
01:09:11,092 --> 01:09:15,172
He likens the population to insects,
says we revel in cruelty,

753
01:09:15,252 --> 01:09:17,772
